QuestData.Title: The Nether Disruptor
QuestData.Description:
Well done $n. In testament to the efforts of all forces fighting here, we have come together to complete the construction of the Nether Disruptor.
All that remains is for you to inspect our work, and complete the construction.
QuestData.LogDescription: Complete the construction of the Nether Disruptor.

Objectives.Objective: Complete Construction of the Nether Disruptor
